<br>
I didn't use PA on the dunters or tree.  Actually, the tree jumped me when I wasn't ready.  For the dunters, I was pulling with a xbow and just waiting for them to get to me.  Most of the time I evaded their first swing and opened with Hamstring/Leaper.  I evaded a LOT and HS/L chain was devastating and didn't use much endurance. <p><font size=1>
